<template>
  hola
</template>

<script>
import { onMounted } from 'vue'
import { useStore } from 'vuex'
export default {
    name: 'VerCarrito',
    setup(){
        const store = useStore()
        const carrito = {}
        onMounted (()=> {
            carrito = store.state.carrito
        });
        return {
            carrito
        }
    }
}
</script>
